Technical Document 3 — Osint & Social Media Identification Methodology
1. Introduction
This section outlines the proposed approach for identifying 20–30 informal-sector businesses in Ghana using publicly available data sources, WhatsApp verification, and basic pattern recognition algorithms.
Core Principle: Use only public data + WhatsApp-based validation to build a business database that feeds the officer dashboard.

2. What is OSINT for Tax Identification?
OSINT (Open-Source Intelligence) = gathering business information from publicly accessible sources without breaching privacy laws.
